summary: A realistic FXAA setting that makes Skyrim look overall more dark and cold...
descriptionHtml:
[b]Description:[/b]
A realistic FXAA setting that makes Skyrim look overall more dark and cold. Look at the screenshots for a comparison. 

[b]Installation:[/b]
Place the folder in your Skyrim folder (not Skyrim/data) and override all files if it asks. 


Made by using [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/131]FXAA Post Process Injector[/url], thanks to Retspadez for uploading it.
